2 teaspone oil
4 cloves of garlic
1/2 ginger
fry a little bit the ginger and garlic
take 2 onions and tomatos and make a pure
when the garlic and ginger is golden brown then add tamato and onion pure
after this add 1 teaspone cumin powder
3 teaspone coriander powder
3 teaspone red chili power '
and 4 teaspone rajma masala
cover the mix and when it wil lose oil pour it into the boiled beans 
pour water according to the beans and cook it in low flame 
after this add salt accordingto your taste 
and our dish is ready

take rice (you can any amount)
add water , cumin , and ghee 
cook for 30 mins and its done 